    "description": "REA India Holdings Services has an exciting opening for a Senior Property Advisor at our Pune office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout REA India Holdings Services:\nREA India Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Maintain a pipeline of qualified leads using CRM software\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Prepare presentations and proposals for institutional clients\n• Conduct market research and provide competitive analysis\n• Conduct land acquisition due diligence and feasibility studies\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Lease Administration\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in Contract Management\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Real Estate Law\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Learning & development budget\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with REA India Holdings Services!",
